name: An Elephant Journey
description:
This is the story of how an asian elephant that lived all her life in captivity in Argentina was transferred in the middle of Covid-19 lockdown to a new home at an elephant sanctuary in Chapada de Guimaraes, Brasil. 
4.33 am. Concordia - Argentina. This is our first stop to check on Mara since we left the zoo. The three caregivers open a small door in the front of the transfer box. Mara curiously poked her trunk out to sniff the surroundings.
